English names of the first 10000 powers of 10

European System without dashes

For the names of larger numbers, or numbers that are not a power of 10, see the following:

  • See "How high can you count?" for an explanation of the European counting system.
  • The English names in this table were produced by the name of a number program. The source that program is also available.

There are other "first 10000 powers of 10" tables available:

  • American system with dashes
  • American system without dashes
  • Eurpoean system with dashes
  • Eurpoean system without dashes
